childAltar.hintText: 3 Spiritual Stones found in Hyrule...^$0Jabu-Jabu's Belly...^$1Link's Pocket...^$2Deku Tree...^$iYe who may become a Hero...&Offer the spiritual stones and&play the Song of Time.

adultAltar.hintText: An awakening voice from the Sacred&Realm will call those destined to be&Sages, who dwell in the five temples.^$8Dodongo's Cavern...^$3Fire Temple...^$4Water Temple...^$5Shadow Temple...^$6Spirit Temple...^$7Forest Temple...^$lThe awakened ones require&the Shadow and Spirit Medallions&as well as the Light Arrows.^$bAnd the %revil one%w's key will&be kept in a big chest&%rinside its tower%w.^$kTogether with the Hero of Time,&the awakened ones will return&the light of peace to the world...
